<h4>Share a valuable resource :</h4>
<form class="formdiv" action="/res" method="post">
    &nbsp;&nbsp;
    <label for="title">Title: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</label>
    <input name="title" placeholder="Enter the title of the stuff to be posted" maxlength="90" required></input>
    <br /><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;
    <label for="desc">Description:&nbsp;</label>
    <input name="desc" placeholder="Enter a brief description of the stuff to be posted"
        maxlength="700" required></input>
    <br /><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;
    <label for="link">Link: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</label>
    <input name="link" placeholder="Enter the location link of the stuff to be posted (like a link of an article) " maxlength="500"
        required></input>
    <br /><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;
    <label for="thumb">Thumbnail: &nbsp;</label>
    <input name="thumb" placeholder="Enter the photo location link to used as thumbnail (like direct image link from imgbb)"
        maxlength="500" required></input>
    <br /><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;
    Hint: You can upload an image on <a href="https://imgbb.com/upload" target="_blank">imgbb</a> and get its <i>direct
        link</i> or fill in <i>https://i.ibb.co/HBHm0Vr/gallery.png</i>
    <br /><br />&nbsp;&nbsp;
    <button class="menuElement" type="submit">Submit</button>
</form>

